## D1 Schema

```sql
CREATE TABLE tenants (
  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
  name TEXT NOT NULL,
  email TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  password_hash TEXT NOT NULL,
  brp_api_url TEXT,
