## Mock BRP API (for development)

Create a mock server (can be a simple Worker route at `/mock/brp/*`) that simulates the BRP API:

- 3 locations (Aarhus, Copenhagen, Odense)
- 8-10 products across categories (memberships, punchcards, trials)
- Member lookup that returns "found" for test@test.com, "not found" for anything else
- Payment link creation that returns a fake URL
- Realistic response shapes and delays (200-500ms)

This lets us build the entire frontend without BRP access and swap in the real API later.

