## Deployment

### Cloudflare setup
- One Workers project for the API proxy + admin API
- Two Pages projects: one for checkout SPA, one for admin panel
- D1 database for tenant data
- KV namespace for domain mapping and product caching
- R2 bucket for logo uploads (optional, can use base64 in D1 for MVP)

### Environment
- `dev`: local Wrangler dev server with mock BRP API
- `staging`: deployed to Cloudflare with mock BRP
- `production`: deployed with real BRP connections

### Domain structure (platform-owned)
- `admin.brpfront.dk` - admin panel
- `preview-{tenantId}.brpfront.dk` - preview URLs
- Custom domains via Cloudflare for SaaS

