## What NOT to build in MVP

- No analytics dashboard (just support GA via measurement ID)
- No A/B testing
- No email notifications or transactional emails
- No multi-user accounts (one login per tenant)
- No billing/subscription management (handle payments manually or via Stripe later)
- No event/class booking flows (memberships, punchcards, trials only)
- No drag-and-drop page builder
- No internationalization (Danish only for MVP)
- No Mailchimp or email marketing integrations